Job Details
1. Prepare Functional Manuals, User manuals, software specification documents
2. Complete writing assignments according to set standards regarding order, clarity, consciences, style and terminology
3. Ability to attend internal and external meetings and prepare meeting minutes.
4. Produce high-quality documentation that meets applicable standards and is appropriate for its intended audience.
Requirements
1 + years of experience in technical writing of software documentationAbility to deliver high quality documentation paying attention to detailAbility to quickly grasp complex technical concepts and make them easily understandable in text and pictures.
Excellent written skills in English.
